        <h1>Project Specification: Custom RAG Tool for Medical Device Regulations</h1>
        <p>For BRM Extremities (Italy) – Built by Choyon (@thechoyon) on Fiverr</p>
        <p class="lead">Empowering global expansion with AI-driven compliance insights for orthopedic innovations. Inspired by <a href="https://github.com/harindermashiana/sec-10q-rag" target="_blank" style="color: #ffd700; text-decoration: underline;">harindermashiana/sec-10q-rag</a> GitHub repo.</p>
